                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Cattappirakaraṇam</title>. Cf. <title>Madras Tamil Lexicon</title>, s.v.:  <quote rend="block">சத்தப்பிரகரணம் catta-p-pirakaraṇam, n. saptan +. A treatise on Vēdānta in seven chapters or parts; ஒரு வேதாந்தநூல்.</quote></p>
<p>The text is incomplete: it contains only the first four <foreign xml:lang="sa">prakaraṇam</foreign>s (the 4th being incomplete).</p> 
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (August 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      
</summary>
                  
